import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App';
import "../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import { HashRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
<Router>
  <App/>
</Router>,document.getElementById("root")
)
